			<h4><a rel="nofollow" id="comment_link_64660208" name="comment_link_64660208" href="//tech.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23401972&amp;cid=64660208" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64660208)" >Re:</a>


